1
00:00:44,362 --> 00:00:49,137
=The Hidden Heir Ye Chen=
(Adapted from "The Peerless Son-in-Law")

2
00:00:49,650 --> 00:00:52,237
=Episode 2=

3
00:01:07,200 --> 00:01:07,990
- Mr. Ye!
- Mr. Ye!

4
00:01:09,600 --> 00:01:10,280
Mr. Ye,

5
00:01:10,480 --> 00:01:11,319
you're not dreaming.

6
00:01:11,680 --> 00:01:12,599
Mr. Tang saved you.

7
00:01:15,879 --> 00:01:16,850
(Mr. Tang?)

8
00:01:22,319 --> 00:01:23,439
(He's so cool.)

9
00:01:23,920 --> 00:01:25,799
(How can he be cooler than me?)

10
00:01:26,962 --> 00:01:29,062
(Tang Sihai, Dihao Group's founder)

11
00:01:29,560 --> 00:01:30,200
Mr. Ye,

12
00:01:30,400 --> 00:01:31,760
welcome home.

13
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:32,840
Thanks.

14
00:01:32,840 --> 00:01:33,920
You're welcome, Mr. Ye.

15
00:01:34,599 --> 00:01:35,239
Protecting you

16
00:01:35,799 --> 00:01:36,959
is what I should do.

17
00:01:37,159 --> 00:01:39,560
But why do you address me
with such respect?

18
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:45,799
Mr. Ye.

19
00:01:47,400 --> 00:01:48,799
Because you've always been

20
00:01:48,800 --> 00:01:50,280
the heir to the Ye family in Yanjing.

21
00:01:50,719 --> 00:01:51,359
Me?

22
00:01:52,760 --> 00:01:53,799
The heir to the Ye family?

23
00:01:54,319 --> 00:01:55,079
That's right.

24
00:01:55,487 --> 00:01:58,537
The most prestigious
Ye family in all of Huaxia.

25
00:02:00,462 --> 00:02:01,503
A couple of lunatics.

26
00:02:03,519 --> 00:02:04,040
Alright.

27
00:02:04,660 --> 00:02:05,599
I need to deliver food.

28
00:02:07,239 --> 00:02:08,159
Let's talk later.

29
00:02:08,159 --> 00:02:09,120
Don't hold me up.

30
00:02:27,062 --> 00:02:29,280
This is your father, Ye Changying,

31
00:02:29,525 --> 00:02:31,013
and your mother, An Chengxi.

32
00:02:45,037 --> 00:02:45,838
Your parents

33
00:02:45,838 --> 00:02:48,500
passed away
in that car accident years ago.

34
00:02:49,039 --> 00:02:50,439
You suffered a head injury.

35
00:02:50,680 --> 00:02:51,599
You've forgotten

36
00:02:51,879 --> 00:02:52,879
many things.

37
00:02:53,159 --> 00:02:54,000
Wait a minute.

38
00:02:57,479 --> 00:02:59,000
If I'm really such a mighty heir,

39
00:03:00,100 --> 00:03:01,491
how did I end up like this?

40
00:03:02,037 --> 00:03:03,797
Because your parents' marriage

41
00:03:03,919 --> 00:03:05,439
wasn't approved by the family.

42
00:03:05,900 --> 00:03:07,680
Mr. Tang
was a good friend of your parents

43
00:03:07,680 --> 00:03:09,500
and also the former butler
of the Ye family.

44
00:03:09,639 --> 00:03:11,759
He entrusted you
to Madam Li to raise you.

45
00:03:12,159 --> 00:03:13,159
That's right.

46
00:03:17,075 --> 00:03:19,834
Big families have their own conflicts.

47
00:03:20,575 --> 00:03:21,375
But you

48
00:03:21,759 --> 00:03:23,280
are Ye Changying's son.

49
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:24,560
So

50
00:03:24,719 --> 00:03:27,319
you have to take back

51
00:03:27,599 --> 00:03:28,759
what was always yours.

52
00:03:29,639 --> 00:03:30,639
I'm Wang Dongxue.

53
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:34,280
You mean the chairperson of Dihao Group?

54
00:03:39,750 --> 00:03:42,750
(Wang Dongxue,
Dihao Group's chairperson)

55
00:03:43,050 --> 00:03:44,529
You don't look like her.

56
00:03:45,159 --> 00:03:45,960
The photo's edited?

57
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:50,439
Mr. Tang founded Dihao Group.

58
00:03:50,919 --> 00:03:52,120
But for safety's sake,

59
00:03:52,439 --> 00:03:54,080
we ask that you keep your identity

60
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:55,039
secret for now.

61
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:56,319
Mr. Ye,

62
00:03:57,159 --> 00:04:00,000
we've suddenly told you so much today.

63
00:04:00,562 --> 00:04:03,042
You probably
can't accept it all at once.

64
00:04:03,150 --> 00:04:04,110
Oh, not at all.

65
00:04:04,637 --> 00:04:05,625
I can totally accept it.

66
00:04:08,200 --> 00:04:09,080
I can keep it secret.

67
00:04:09,537 --> 00:04:10,463
But

68
00:04:10,960 --> 00:04:12,639
could you help me with something?

69
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:16,039
Whatever it is, just ask.

70
00:04:17,280 --> 00:04:18,560
I just want...

71
00:04:25,120 --> 00:04:26,040
Sharp.

72
00:04:29,825 --> 00:04:30,700
(Birthday)

73
00:04:30,759 --> 00:04:32,800
It's just a two-billion-yuan project
with Dihao.

74
00:04:33,337 --> 00:04:34,575
If I want to meet Wang Dongxue,

75
00:04:34,575 --> 00:04:35,759
I can meet her anytime.

76
00:04:35,920 --> 00:04:36,560
That deal?

77
00:04:36,879 --> 00:04:39,319
I can land it for Churan in no time.

78
00:04:40,439 --> 00:04:41,839
Ye Chen! Master Ye!

79
00:04:41,839 --> 00:04:43,680
You're our lucky star!

80
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:45,079
Please forgive me.

81
00:05:07,925 --> 00:05:10,237
(Birthday)

82
00:05:14,959 --> 00:05:16,439
Are you seriously daydreaming here?

83
00:05:16,439 --> 00:05:17,959
Stop talking nonsense.

84
00:05:17,959 --> 00:05:18,959
You piece of trash.

85
00:05:18,959 --> 00:05:20,040
You must be drunk.

86
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:21,399
Ye Chen.

87
00:05:23,160 --> 00:05:24,160
Stop messing around.

88
00:05:25,879 --> 00:05:27,439
Just sign the contract.

89
00:05:28,959 --> 00:05:29,720
Ye Chen.

90
00:05:34,519 --> 00:05:36,600
Once you sign,
this million yuan is yours.

91
00:05:55,387 --> 00:05:57,079
Madam Li's surgery is done.

92
00:05:57,079 --> 00:05:57,930
And it went smoothly.

93
00:05:58,160 --> 00:05:59,079
No way.

94
00:05:59,079 --> 00:06:00,439
That's absolutely impossible.

95
00:06:04,040 --> 00:06:05,637
Who arranged the surgery for you?

96
00:06:05,712 --> 00:06:07,062
None of your business.

97
00:06:07,275 --> 00:06:07,839
Zhang Wenhao,

98
00:06:08,199 --> 00:06:09,120
dare to bet with me?

99
00:06:11,240 --> 00:06:12,639
Get to the point.

100
00:06:13,480 --> 00:06:14,240
I'll help Churan.

101
00:06:15,199 --> 00:06:16,000
You help Xiao Weiwei.

102
00:06:16,525 --> 00:06:17,775
Let's see who gets the deal

103
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:19,399
with Dihao first.

104
00:06:20,079 --> 00:06:21,319
If I win,

105
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:23,360
you can't bother Churan again.

106
00:06:24,562 --> 00:06:26,145
And all of you can't bully her either.

107
00:06:26,487 --> 00:06:27,720
If I lose,

108
00:06:27,959 --> 00:06:30,125
I'll sign the divorce papers immediately

109
00:06:30,125 --> 00:06:31,190
and leave the Xiao family.

110
00:06:31,225 --> 00:06:33,150
I accept this bet.

111
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:35,759
Ye Chen will definitely lose.

112
00:06:37,825 --> 00:06:39,167
We'll see about that.

113
00:06:41,237 --> 00:06:42,079
- No, Mom.
- Scram!

114
00:06:42,079 --> 00:06:42,800
Don't call me Mom!

115
00:06:42,937 --> 00:06:43,680
Scram!

116
00:06:43,762 --> 00:06:44,680
Mom.

117
00:06:44,875 --> 00:06:46,199
Can you stop shouting?

118
00:06:46,275 --> 00:06:48,079
It's embarrassing if the neighbors hear.

119
00:06:48,439 --> 00:06:50,720
- What if he...
- That's not possible!

120
00:06:50,720 --> 00:06:51,537
Mom,

121
00:06:51,720 --> 00:06:52,519
the bet's on.

122
00:06:52,519 --> 00:06:53,425
Let's see what happens.

123
00:06:53,839 --> 00:06:55,160
Go back and rest, okay?

124
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:57,175
Sit down and relax. It's fine.

125
00:07:05,879 --> 00:07:06,639
How are you?

126
00:07:06,959 --> 00:07:07,720
Are you hurt?

127
00:07:09,319 --> 00:07:10,439
When Lan

128
00:07:10,519 --> 00:07:12,240
married me,

129
00:07:12,240 --> 00:07:14,190
she thought she was
marrying into a rich family.

130
00:07:14,680 --> 00:07:16,839
But she didn't expect that I don't have

131
00:07:17,650 --> 00:07:18,945
much status in this family.

132
00:07:19,400 --> 00:07:22,001
She's afraid Churan
will end up like her.

133
00:07:24,160 --> 00:07:25,160
I'm fine, Dad.

134
00:07:33,162 --> 00:07:34,839
- Ye Chen.
- Yes?

135
00:07:35,225 --> 00:07:37,037
Why did you bet

136
00:07:37,037 --> 00:07:37,837
with Zhang Wenhao?

137
00:07:39,800 --> 00:07:42,160
Because I have full confidence
in your ability to win.

138
00:07:42,900 --> 00:07:44,600
We don't have resources or connections.

139
00:07:44,850 --> 00:07:46,290
Even if my proposal is great,

140
00:07:46,290 --> 00:07:47,449
she won't use mine. We...

141
00:07:47,519 --> 00:07:49,240
Who says we don't have connections?

142
00:07:50,400 --> 00:07:52,312
I'll get Wang Dongxue to meet you.

143
00:07:58,240 --> 00:07:59,680
Are you okay?

144
00:08:01,920 --> 00:08:03,319
Don't worry. I'm fine.

145
00:08:03,319 --> 00:08:04,199
I'm great.

146
00:08:07,439 --> 00:08:08,439
By the way,

147
00:08:08,959 --> 00:08:10,959
what's the deal with Madam Li's surgery?

148
00:08:11,639 --> 00:08:13,319
You'll find out soon enough.

149
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:16,759
Why are you smiling so much today?

150
00:08:17,079 --> 00:08:18,360
I've always liked to smile.

151
00:08:19,399 --> 00:08:20,759
Churan, let me ask you.

152
00:08:21,199 --> 00:08:23,959
If one day I become super rich,

153
00:08:24,079 --> 00:08:25,360
like, ridiculously rich,

154
00:08:25,680 --> 00:08:26,759
beyond rich,

155
00:08:27,160 --> 00:08:28,879
like I can buy anything I want...

156
00:08:28,879 --> 00:08:30,600
What do you want to say?

157
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:34,040
I just wanted to ask,

158
00:08:34,040 --> 00:08:35,500
what would you want to do the most?

159
00:08:42,679 --> 00:08:43,840
Xiao Group

160
00:08:44,399 --> 00:08:46,120
is my grandpa's legacy.

161
00:08:46,687 --> 00:08:48,916
I can't just watch it get destroyed.

162
00:08:51,240 --> 00:08:52,519
So no matter what,

163
00:08:53,987 --> 00:08:55,107
I won't give up.

164
00:08:57,799 --> 00:08:58,200
Alright.

165
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:00,080
Got it.

166
00:09:00,960 --> 00:09:02,012
From now on,

167
00:09:04,320 --> 00:09:05,950
this is the goal I'm working toward.

168
00:09:16,575 --> 00:09:20,012
(Entertainment effects,
please do not imitate)

169
00:09:20,080 --> 00:09:21,279
You really came?

170
00:09:21,279 --> 00:09:22,840
Your nerve is something else.

171
00:09:23,159 --> 00:09:24,440
How dare you come to Dihao Group

172
00:09:24,575 --> 00:09:26,975
riding a crappy e-bike

173
00:09:27,039 --> 00:09:28,039
and wearing zero jewels?

174
00:09:28,240 --> 00:09:28,759
Ye Chen,

175
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:30,037
let me give you a hand.

176
00:09:30,559 --> 00:09:31,850
Sell this plastic bottle.

177
00:09:32,137 --> 00:09:34,150
You could make 3,000 yuan
a month with some effort.

178
00:09:38,240 --> 00:09:38,600
Let's go.

179
00:09:39,559 --> 00:09:41,159
Trash should stay in the trash can.

180
00:09:44,210 --> 00:09:45,279
I'm here for Wang Dongxue.

181
00:09:48,500 --> 00:09:49,390
Tang Sihai will do too.

182
00:09:55,720 --> 00:09:56,559
I'm Ye Chen.

183
00:09:58,787 --> 00:09:59,799
Ye Chen's here.

184
00:10:04,050 --> 00:10:05,120
They're here to welcome me.

185
00:10:07,360 --> 00:10:07,879
What?

186
00:10:10,200 --> 00:10:10,879
Ye Chen.

187
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:11,759
Put him down.

188
00:10:12,440 --> 00:10:13,519
Or I'll call the cops.

189
00:10:17,519 --> 00:10:18,360
Are you okay?

190
00:10:20,039 --> 00:10:20,840
Hello,

191
00:10:21,120 --> 00:10:22,180
I'm Ms. Wang's secretary.

192
00:10:22,879 --> 00:10:24,039
She's waiting for you.

193
00:10:30,240 --> 00:10:31,360
Hello, Ms. Xiao.

194
00:10:35,159 --> 00:10:36,360
Hello, Ms. Wang.

195
00:10:37,312 --> 00:10:38,672
This is Churan's proposal.

196
00:10:38,840 --> 00:10:39,737
Please take a look.

197
00:10:43,220 --> 00:10:44,519
Let's go straight to the meeting.

198
00:10:46,200 --> 00:10:46,600
Sure.

199
00:10:47,159 --> 00:10:47,720
(Dihao Group)
Hello, everyone.

200
00:10:48,039 --> 00:10:49,679
I'm Xiao Churan from Xiao Group.

201
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:51,159
(Restructuring Holiday Life)
Today, I'll be presenting

202
00:10:51,159 --> 00:10:54,240
the Jinxi Resort Planning Proposal
on restructuring holiday life.

203
00:10:54,519 --> 00:10:56,399
(Design Principles)
Eco-friendly and cost-effective

204
00:10:56,399 --> 00:10:57,925
are the core principles of my design.

205
00:11:08,559 --> 00:11:10,200
What do you think of Churan's proposal?

206
00:11:10,600 --> 00:11:12,120
Pretty professional. It's very mature.

207
00:11:13,159 --> 00:11:14,559
Do you think she can land the deal

208
00:11:14,559 --> 00:11:15,512
with her proposal?

209
00:11:15,799 --> 00:11:16,519
Of course.

210
00:11:18,519 --> 00:11:19,440
Skip all the procedures.

211
00:11:19,600 --> 00:11:20,320
Give her the deal.

212
00:11:20,519 --> 00:11:21,600
Okay, I'll handle it.

213
00:11:21,879 --> 00:11:23,159
Sihai, you're a true buddy.

214
00:11:24,080 --> 00:11:25,100
It's just a small project.

215
00:11:25,110 --> 00:11:26,200
Doesn't matter who handles it.

216
00:11:26,200 --> 00:11:27,000
Don't forget.

217
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:29,159
The entire Dihao belongs to you, Mr. Ye.

218
00:11:29,519 --> 00:11:30,320
- Ye Chen.
- Mine?

219
00:11:33,279 --> 00:11:33,960
Why are you here?

220
00:11:34,200 --> 00:11:35,440
My presentation's done.

221
00:11:35,559 --> 00:11:36,600
They're discussing it now.

222
00:11:41,080 --> 00:11:42,399
Who's this?

223
00:11:43,440 --> 00:11:44,519
Mr. Tang.

224
00:11:45,120 --> 00:11:46,639
He's Dihao Group's...

225
00:11:48,879 --> 00:11:50,279
top janitor.

226
00:11:51,120 --> 00:11:52,799
He's worth around 800 billion yuan.

227
00:11:53,200 --> 00:11:54,000
He just won't rest.

228
00:11:54,279 --> 00:11:55,600
He drives a Ferrari

229
00:11:55,600 --> 00:11:56,919
but comes here to mop the floors.

230
00:11:56,919 --> 00:11:57,919
Weird, right?

231
00:11:58,679 --> 00:12:00,320
How did you know him, then?

232
00:12:02,519 --> 00:12:04,360
The first time I saw him,

233
00:12:04,360 --> 00:12:06,240
he was passed out drunk on the sidewalk.

234
00:12:06,679 --> 00:12:08,600
Lucky for him,
I happened to be a very kind soul

235
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:09,200
and saved him.

236
00:12:09,320 --> 00:12:11,712
He helped arrange Madam Li's surgery.

237
00:12:13,559 --> 00:12:15,600
We basically helped each other.

238
00:12:17,039 --> 00:12:19,080
Mr. Tang, thank you.

239
00:12:19,799 --> 00:12:21,159
He has poor hearing.

240
00:12:25,639 --> 00:12:27,700
Mr. Tang, thank you!

241
00:12:29,120 --> 00:12:29,840
They knew?

242
00:12:30,360 --> 00:12:31,759
I said thank you.

243
00:12:31,759 --> 00:12:32,700
The shoe?

244
00:12:32,800 --> 00:12:34,521
- Thank you.
- Value?

245
00:12:34,521 --> 00:12:36,200
- Thank you.
- Take you?

246
00:12:37,240 --> 00:12:39,037
He's always like this.

247
00:12:41,399 --> 00:12:42,240
Yunfei,

248
00:12:42,759 --> 00:12:43,519
do you think

249
00:12:43,519 --> 00:12:45,519
they actually met Ms. Wang?

250
00:12:45,519 --> 00:12:46,279
No way.

251
00:12:46,279 --> 00:12:47,440
How could Dihao Group

252
00:12:47,440 --> 00:12:49,240
work with those bottom-tier trash?

253
00:12:49,240 --> 00:12:50,399
Who are you calling trash?

254
00:12:51,759 --> 00:12:52,159
You.

255
00:12:52,240 --> 00:12:53,600
Well, you did get one thing right.

256
00:12:54,112 --> 00:12:56,962
Dihao definitely won't work
with bottom-tier trash.

257
00:12:58,087 --> 00:12:59,159
What are you doing?

258
00:12:59,159 --> 00:13:00,610
I'm here for a meeting with Ms. Wang.

259
00:13:00,679 --> 00:13:01,480
Yunfei.

260
00:13:02,440 --> 00:13:03,399
I'm not your daddy.

261
00:13:03,399 --> 00:13:04,230
Why are you bowing to me?

262
00:13:04,240 --> 00:13:05,679
Do you know who I am?

263
00:13:06,279 --> 00:13:07,537
Okay, I'll shut up.

264
00:13:08,000 --> 00:13:09,080
Let me introduce you.

265
00:13:09,320 --> 00:13:11,639
This is the eldest son
of the Wang family,

266
00:13:11,725 --> 00:13:14,175
the lowest-tier partner of Dihao Group.

267
00:13:14,180 --> 00:13:15,990
He doesn't look like
anything special either.

268
00:13:19,120 --> 00:13:20,279
Ms. Jiang, it's me.

269
00:13:20,639 --> 00:13:21,399
Wang Yunfei.

270
00:13:21,720 --> 00:13:22,759
Mr. Zhang Wenhao

271
00:13:22,759 --> 00:13:24,440
introduced me to visit you and Ms. Wang.

272
00:13:24,440 --> 00:13:25,612
Hello, Ms. Jiang.

273
00:13:27,450 --> 00:13:28,120
Ms. Xiao,

274
00:13:28,440 --> 00:13:30,700
sorry for letting these pests disturb you.

275
00:13:31,039 --> 00:13:33,000
Ms. Wang is very satisfied
with your proposal.

276
00:13:33,159 --> 00:13:34,240
(Letter of Intent)
Here's the letter of intent.

277
00:13:34,559 --> 00:13:35,240
Please accept it.

278
00:13:42,200 --> 00:13:42,840
Thank you.

279
00:13:44,320 --> 00:13:45,159
Ms. Wang

280
00:13:45,159 --> 00:13:46,600
also has a message for you two.

281
00:13:46,720 --> 00:13:47,480
From now on,

282
00:13:47,840 --> 00:13:50,320
every single contract between us
is terminated.

283
00:13:50,399 --> 00:13:51,320
At Dihao,

284
00:13:51,480 --> 00:13:53,600
we don't work with worthless trash.

285
00:13:53,620 --> 00:13:54,705
I want to see Wang Dongxue.

286
00:13:54,705 --> 00:13:55,879
I want to talk to her in person.

287
00:13:55,879 --> 00:13:58,200
She's very busy.
She has no time for trash.

288
00:13:58,720 --> 00:13:59,240
Yeah.

289
00:13:59,559 --> 00:14:01,960
Trash should stay in the trash can.

290
00:14:03,240 --> 00:14:04,000
Don't!

291
00:14:04,000 --> 00:14:04,759
What are you doing?

292
00:14:04,759 --> 00:14:05,690
What are you guys doing?

293
00:14:05,750 --> 00:14:06,870
(Those two losers.)

294
00:14:09,937 --> 00:14:11,450
(First blood)

295
00:14:11,561 --> 00:14:12,840
If I can't do it,

296
00:14:12,840 --> 00:14:13,879
I'll leave the Xiao family

297
00:14:14,000 --> 00:14:15,200
and Churan

298
00:14:15,200 --> 00:14:17,600
and kneel in front of you.

299
00:14:17,720 --> 00:14:19,159
As you predicted,

300
00:14:19,159 --> 00:14:20,679
Ye Chen has already taken the bait.

301
00:14:20,960 --> 00:14:23,062
Let the hook sink deeper.

302
00:14:40,412 --> 00:14:42,900
♪They said I was only meant
to gaze at the light♪

303
00:14:42,987 --> 00:14:46,740
♪Never knowing I am the flame itself♪

304
00:14:47,200 --> 00:14:52,137
♪I am fireworks, not a fire cast aside♪

305
00:14:52,300 --> 00:14:54,587
♪I open my eyes amid the ruins♪

306
00:14:54,900 --> 00:14:57,580
♪No one shields me
from the wind or the sky♪

307
00:14:58,650 --> 00:15:01,275
♪Let them mock, let them sneer♪

308
00:15:01,575 --> 00:15:04,587
♪I sharpen my silence into blades♪

309
00:15:04,787 --> 00:15:07,837
♪Every cold word, I remember♪

310
00:15:07,950 --> 00:15:10,912
♪Etching my path of defiance
into my heart♪

311
00:15:11,180 --> 00:15:14,337
♪Fate did not sign my future for me♪

312
00:15:14,562 --> 00:15:18,312
♪I carved my own light
with clenched fists♪

313
00:15:18,312 --> 00:15:21,175
♪I belong to no one♪

314
00:15:21,237 --> 00:15:24,687
♪I am the ember
that refuses to bow to destiny♪

315
00:15:24,687 --> 00:15:27,362
♪Even if the world burns me into ash♪

316
00:15:27,362 --> 00:15:33,700
♪I will rise upon those ashes♪
